name: Cover of the online-magazine lyuk.media
description: Hey! We are a community of journalists and artists who are working on the creation of a magazine about culture and human rights. We love art, memes and different forms of storytelling. This art is a cover for the story about NFT exhibition “POLEMAKIV” in Kharkiv, Ukraine.   https://lyuk.media/city/POLEMAKIV/  Made by Ekaterina Drozd
